lines.text: [slaps each other five high on the ceiling and then run into the Skelevator]
Hey, w-w-what do I look like, a t-t-trampoline?
The Ghostbusters are out right now. Outta their minds, that is!
You've reached the Ghostbusters and you're in luck... they're not here!

[after one of his numerous crashes into a wall]
It isn't fair, all the other ghosts can go through walls.
